Text:
Thanks!

"McCartney I" is a pure Paul McCartney without any George Martin and other orchestra maneuvers. It is valued because of this.

As for "Wild Life" I don't understand why you joined such different works into a one set.
Thanks so much for this....it's nice to find conscientious uploaders who take the time to put up lossless and tag things with at least some sort of rationale :)
